    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Books in which to keep records of a child's birth and development through infancy, usually in the form of an album to hold pictures and other memorabilia as well as text.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
